{"tid":914054,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[蘋果日報] 文革冤魂劉少奇誕辰120週年前夕，被「追降」為「國家副主席」","createTime":"2018-11-24T02:30:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-12T09:30:41.000Z","uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d363b76480f0b599471d449aaeae4bed93a5e90c","tid":914054,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T02:30:13.000Z","msg":"【蘋果日報】<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181123/58950534\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181123%2F58950534&d=rDITRtNisujewFGBC%2BDvnv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=928c8ee1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181123%2F58950534&h=7e7a78b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181123/58950534</a><br />\n<br />\n在文革中被批鬥至死的<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">國家前<strong>副主席</strong>劉少奇</span></span>（1898年11月24日-1969年11月12日），明天是他的誕辰120周年。<br />\n<br />\n新華社今日報道，中共中央舉行座談會作出高規格紀念，國家主席習近平、中共中央政治局七常委全體出席。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://res.img.ifeng.com/2011/1121/xes_fdd71cdf615ea36f27ce3dcb72447bb2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fres.img.ifeng.com%2F2011%2F1121%2Fxes_fdd71cdf615ea36f27ce3dcb72447bb2.jpg&h=d4e430b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n座談會在人民大會堂舉行，習近平高度評價劉少奇的一生，號召全民學習劉少奇的品德和精神風範。<br />\n<br />\n他並強調：「我們在新的歷史起點上進行偉大鬥爭、建設偉大工程、推進偉大事業、實現偉大夢想，就是劉少奇同志等老一輩革命家一生奮鬥的偉大事業的繼承和發展。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img2.3png.com/35b1d124c5f29192b4bbe67489940484da29.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg2.3png.com%2F35b1d124c5f29192b4bbe67489940484da29.png&h=19a6c1f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n此外，中共中央政治局常委李克強、汪洋、王滬寧、趙樂際、韓正出席座談會，中共中央政治局常委栗戰書主持座談會。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，今年下半年以來，官方紀念劉少奇的活動陸續開展，相關座談會、研討會相繼在北京、上海舉行。<br />\n<br />\n香港蘋果日報（2018年11月23日）"},{"pid":"f1ca82d9fa3713a4e88473a09594b0e2eaec840b","tid":914054,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T05:30:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://news.sohu.com/upload/rmrb49-08/imgb/59-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.sohu.com%2Fupload%2Frmrb49-08%2Fimgb%2F59-1.jpg&h=56a0460c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a7f67692b2dc26c86eb12c858d15d6f4685d75b","tid":914054,"uid":118120,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T05:31:52.000Z","msg":"好似1984咁<br />\n過去既野鐘意點改就點改"},{"pid":"0700dd157b9d4bdfa979c9f3d5e8a5c6552aa288","tid":914054,"uid":3241,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T05:37:57.000Z","msg":"中國歷史就係笑話<br />\n用槍指住史官去寫"},{"pid":"ee6366edc8306e95563f772580cb23af0cbbc72c","tid":914054,"uid":134381,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T09:16:17.000Z","msg":"劉少奇真係偉大 唔知敝黨有幾多人可以有個好似佢咁風光既結局呢？"},{"pid":"e1affd403dbf77407d1afb912eca2253a41e30a1","tid":914054,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"0700dd157b9d4bdfa979c9f3d5e8a5c6552aa288","tid":914054,"uid":3241,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T05:37:57.000Z","msg":"中國歷史就係笑話<br />\n用槍指住史官去寫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T09:32:34.000Z","msg":"咪傻啦歷史學家都係自己人嚟"},{"pid":"1f47f8aaf4988172eaae449d9c55b6e699fb9dfa","tid":914054,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T09:46:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 重點都係要接受西方思想, 如果黃種人諗果套work二戰就唔會輸啦, 直接借鏡西方, 最好借埋d白人返黎用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f212bc7dbb57cf352bf8eb245fad779ffe53343","tid":914054,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a7f67692b2dc26c86eb12c858d15d6f4685d75b","tid":914054,"uid":118120,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T05:31:52.000Z","msg":"好似1984咁<br />\n過去既野鐘意點改就點改"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"